WEBVTT

00:00:02.600 --> 00:00:04.430
Well, good

00:00:04.440 --> 00:00:05.950
evening, family. Thank you for joining

00:00:05.960 --> 00:00:07.990
me again today. We're going to go

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:09.950
ahead and pray, and

00:00:09.950 --> 00:00:09.960
then

00:00:09.960 --> 00:00:11.870
go over some of the things the Lord

00:00:11.880 --> 00:00:15.630
showed us yesterday in prayer.

00:00:15.640 --> 00:00:18.510
It's been

00:00:18.520 --> 00:00:21.550
amazing praying over

00:00:21.560 --> 00:00:23.670
President Trump and

00:00:31.840 --> 00:00:33.350
the Valley of Decision

00:00:33.360 --> 00:00:35.990
concerning where we are as a nation.

00:00:37.640 --> 00:00:41.350
As yesterday's prayer time

00:00:41.360 --> 00:00:44.150
ended, I had more time

00:00:44.160 --> 00:00:45.630
praying and talking to the Lord

00:00:45.640 --> 00:00:49.390
about it. He took the puzzle pieces

00:00:49.400 --> 00:00:51.190
of everything we have been praying

00:00:51.200 --> 00:00:53.830
over since October

00:00:53.840 --> 00:00:55.870
and started putting them

00:00:55.880 --> 00:00:58.110
together regarding where we are in the Valley

00:00:58.120 --> 00:01:00.030
of Decision

00:01:00.040 --> 00:01:01.590
concerning President Trump and the

00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:04.229
decisions he's making. He

00:01:04.229 --> 00:01:04.239
even

00:01:04.239 --> 00:01:08.070
stated that he is

00:01:08.080 --> 00:01:11.030
a businessman before he is the president,

00:01:11.040 --> 00:01:12.550
which I thought was an interesting

00:01:12.560 --> 00:01:15.430
statement because he is running it like

00:01:15.440 --> 00:01:17.070
a business.

00:01:17.080 --> 00:01:19.670
The decisions he's making are

00:01:19.680 --> 00:01:24.150
strategic in his mind, like the chess match

00:01:24.160 --> 00:01:26.870
I saw him

00:01:26.870 --> 00:01:26.880
playing—how

00:01:26.880 --> 00:01:32.190
to dominate world markets

00:01:32.190 --> 00:01:32.200
and

00:01:32.200 --> 00:01:36.710
the world economy,

00:01:36.720 --> 00:01:40.270
not for mercy,

00:01:40.280 --> 00:01:43.430
but to make America great. Just like he

00:01:43.440 --> 00:01:45.190
has said over and over again, he's not

00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:47.070
thinking about other nations. He has

00:01:47.080 --> 00:01:50.150
strategic allies.

00:01:50.160 --> 00:01:53.110
Who do you become friends with? Who

00:01:53.120 --> 00:01:55.270
do you do business with

00:01:55.280 --> 00:01:59.550
versus who is an enemy of America?

00:01:59.560 --> 00:02:01.230
In doing so,

00:02:01.240 --> 00:02:04.230
people still look at him

00:02:05.960 --> 00:02:08.669
through the wrong lens.

00:02:08.679 --> 00:02:10.990
I come across

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:12.790
very strong about some of the things I

00:02:12.800 --> 00:02:16.750
say. I truly believe when I told you

00:02:21.600 --> 00:02:24.590
what I was praying over about

00:02:24.600 --> 00:02:26.230
'drinking the Kool-Aid'and the things

00:02:26.240 --> 00:02:28.430
I've said, because so many

00:02:28.440 --> 00:02:31.550
people only look at it as

00:02:34.710 --> 00:02:34.720
MAGA.

00:02:36.280 --> 00:02:39.110
I look at Trump as an instrument

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:41.949
being used by the Lord.

00:02:41.959 --> 00:02:45.270
God doesn't make mistakes.

00:02:45.280 --> 00:02:46.830
I was sweeping out my car because I

00:02:46.840 --> 00:02:50.150
like to keep my stuff clean, and

00:02:50.160 --> 00:02:52.510
He said to me, 'Do you believe I

00:02:52.520 --> 00:02:54.990
make

00:02:54.990 --> 00:02:55.000
mistakes?'I

00:02:55.000 --> 00:02:57.630
want to ask

00:02:57.640 --> 00:02:59.190
you all

00:02:59.200 --> 00:03:01.390
a question: Do you

00:03:01.400 --> 00:03:04.110
believe that God makes mistakes in the

00:03:04.120 --> 00:03:06.110
decisions He

00:03:06.110 --> 00:03:06.120
makes?

00:03:06.120 --> 00:03:08.949
Do you believe you

00:03:08.959 --> 00:03:11.110
could be a mistake?

00:03:11.120 --> 00:03:13.150
Do you believe that everything God

00:03:13.160 --> 00:03:17.430
does is strategic?

00:03:17.430 --> 00:03:17.440
Are

00:03:17.440 --> 00:03:21.310
there mistakes in your existence

00:03:21.310 --> 00:03:21.320
or

00:03:21.320 --> 00:03:25.830
your personality?

00:03:25.840 --> 00:03:28.030
Do you think it's just by coincidence

00:03:28.040 --> 00:03:31.710
that you are who you are,

00:03:31.720 --> 00:03:36.270
or is God in everything?

00:03:36.280 --> 00:03:38.310
Does God have a hand in everything? Is

00:03:38.320 --> 00:03:41.390
God really that

00:03:41.400 --> 00:03:42.990
big

00:03:43.000 --> 00:03:45.229
that He knows

00:03:45.239 --> 00:03:48.070
every hair on your head?

00:03:48.080 --> 00:03:49.830
He knows your future better than you

00:03:49.840 --> 00:03:52.070
know your past.

00:03:58.160 --> 00:04:02.590
I saw that a lot of prophetic voices

00:04:02.600 --> 00:04:05.870
in the past have been very selective

00:04:05.870 --> 00:04:05.880
about

00:04:05.880 --> 00:04:07.990
how they relay things, like Brother

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:09.230
Hagin.

00:04:09.240 --> 00:04:12.270
Brother Hagin would only say things that

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:14.310
he was allowed to

00:04:14.320 --> 00:04:16.550
relay;

00:04:16.560 --> 00:04:18.470
the Holy Spirit would

00:04:18.480 --> 00:04:22.070
not allow him to share everything

00:04:22.070 --> 00:04:22.080
he received.

00:04:22.080 --> 00:04:24.870
But his personality, from

00:04:24.870 --> 00:04:24.880
what I

00:04:24.880 --> 00:04:27.390
experienced when I was in heaven,

00:04:27.400 --> 00:04:29.190
is very different. He was a very quiet

00:04:29.200 --> 00:04:30.870
individual.

00:04:30.880 --> 00:04:33.150
Even

00:04:33.150 --> 00:04:33.160
from

00:04:33.160 --> 00:04:34.790
that one encounter—and how

00:04:34.800 --> 00:04:36.830
much can you go by one encounter

00:04:36.830 --> 00:04:36.840
in

00:04:36.840 --> 00:04:38.870
heaven—when

00:04:38.880 --> 00:04:41.030
the Lord allowed me to have a visitation. I'm not talking to the

00:04:41.040 --> 00:04:43.270
dead; let the elevator go to

00:04:43.280 --> 00:04:45.350
the top. I

00:04:45.350 --> 00:04:45.360
had

00:04:45.360 --> 00:04:47.990
a visitation

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:49.870
through a portal, allowing me

00:04:49.870 --> 00:04:49.880
to

00:04:49.880 --> 00:04:52.870
listen and

00:04:52.880 --> 00:04:55.070
talk to the living. They're

00:04:55.080 --> 00:04:56.790
not dead; they're alive.

00:05:00.560 --> 00:05:03.190
'I'm more alive

00:05:03.200 --> 00:05:06.030
now than I've ever

00:05:06.040 --> 00:05:08.430
been,'is

00:05:08.440 --> 00:05:11.630
what she said to me.

00:05:11.640 --> 00:05:14.470
I've processed this a lot.

00:05:14.480 --> 00:05:16.230
The Lord said, 'With the

00:05:16.240 --> 00:05:18.830
personality

00:05:18.840 --> 00:05:22.110
I have created in you over the

00:05:22.120 --> 00:05:24.510
course of your lifetime,

00:05:24.520 --> 00:05:31.670
do you think I made a

00:05:31.670 --> 00:05:31.680
mistake?'I

00:05:31.680 --> 00:05:32.950
said,

00:05:32.960 --> 00:05:34.590
'No, you

00:05:34.590 --> 00:05:34.600
are

00:05:34.600 --> 00:05:36.030
a God who would never make a

00:05:36.040 --> 00:05:37.630
mistake.

00:05:37.640 --> 00:05:39.550
I'm fearfully and wonderfully made in

00:05:39.560 --> 00:05:42.270
Your image.'I know that every person

00:05:42.280 --> 00:05:44.630
here has a special call and

00:05:44.630 --> 00:05:44.640
has

00:05:44.640 --> 00:05:46.310
been chosen for such a time as

00:05:46.320 --> 00:05:47.430
this. Even

00:05:47.430 --> 00:05:47.440
if

00:05:47.440 --> 00:05:49.950
we do things stupidly,

00:05:51.520 --> 00:05:52.990
the footsteps of the

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:55.750
righteous are ordered by the Lord.

00:05:55.760 --> 00:05:57.670
I believe that what the devil meant for

00:05:57.680 --> 00:05:59.630
bad, God will turn around for good

00:05:59.640 --> 00:06:01.830
and your favor immediately if you're

00:06:01.840 --> 00:06:03.350
seeking Him.

00:06:03.360 --> 00:06:05.950
You can't derail your life.

00:06:05.960 --> 00:06:07.950
No matter how bad you think you can mess

00:06:07.960 --> 00:06:10.110
it up, God will turn what the devil

00:06:10.120 --> 00:06:13.190
meant for bad into good

00:06:13.200 --> 00:06:16.110
if you are just seeking Him daily.

00:06:16.120 --> 00:06:18.350
Looking at my

00:06:18.360 --> 00:06:19.950
personality,

00:06:19.960 --> 00:06:23.110
I am very bold. I'm never

00:06:23.120 --> 00:06:24.470
going to back down from anything He tells

00:06:24.480 --> 00:06:26.630
me to say. Even if

00:06:26.640 --> 00:06:28.950
I'm hesitant, I say, 'Here I go,

00:06:28.960 --> 00:06:31.430
I'm going to

00:06:31.430 --> 00:06:31.440
jump.'I

00:06:31.440 --> 00:06:33.190
always tell my kids,

00:06:33.200 --> 00:06:35.270
'Daddy's going to

00:06:35.280 --> 00:06:38.190
jump.'Even

00:06:38.200 --> 00:06:40.790
if it's not the popular

00:06:40.800 --> 00:06:42.150
opinion,

00:06:42.160 --> 00:06:43.670
I'm going to tell you what the Lord

00:06:43.680 --> 00:06:45.350
tells me.

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:47.430
That's why I will

00:06:47.430 --> 00:06:47.440
never

00:06:47.440 --> 00:06:51.150
parrot other prophets.

00:06:51.160 --> 00:06:54.350
I don't parrot words. I hear what He

00:06:54.360 --> 00:06:56.909
tells me and say it with great

00:06:56.919 --> 00:06:58.190
boldness.

00:06:58.200 --> 00:07:00.150
It may mirror

00:07:00.160 --> 00:07:02.670
other prophetic words,

00:07:02.680 --> 00:07:06.350
but my words are not parroted.

00:07:06.360 --> 00:07:09.430
I'm not called to be

00:07:09.440 --> 00:07:11.590
part of an echo; I'm called to be

00:07:11.590 --> 00:07:11.600
a

00:07:11.600 --> 00:07:12.909
voice

00:07:12.919 --> 00:07:16.390
yielded to Him.

00:07:16.400 --> 00:07:18.470
I've asked Him many times if

00:07:18.470 --> 00:07:18.480
He wants

00:07:18.480 --> 00:07:19.990
me to say these things.

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:22.430
He said that

00:07:35.280 --> 00:07:37.909
might have been

00:07:37.909 --> 00:07:37.919
the

00:07:37.919 --> 00:07:44.070
assignment for others back in the '50s through the '90s, but you are a

00:07:44.070 --> 00:07:44.080
'closer.'Their

00:07:44.080 --> 00:07:46.550
assignment was for that

00:07:46.560 --> 00:07:48.230
generation; yours is different for your

00:07:48.240 --> 00:07:49.990
generation.

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:52.070
You cannot compare your call

00:07:52.080 --> 00:07:53.670
or

00:07:53.680 --> 00:07:55.950
your ministry to

00:07:55.960 --> 00:07:57.790
theirs

00:07:57.800 --> 00:08:00.430
because

00:08:00.440 --> 00:08:02.470
they weren't called to say

00:08:02.480 --> 00:08:05.030
what you're called to say.

00:08:05.040 --> 00:08:07.310
Mirroring and comparing like a

00:08:07.320 --> 00:08:08.870
cookie cutter

00:08:08.880 --> 00:08:11.270
is to parrot.

00:08:11.280 --> 00:08:13.190
I've called you to stand out and be

00:08:13.200 --> 00:08:14.830
alone.

00:08:14.840 --> 00:08:17.230
You will say things that maybe even

00:08:17.240 --> 00:08:20.790
the elders don't think you should say.

00:08:20.790 --> 00:08:20.800
Fear

00:08:20.800 --> 00:08:23.110
only what

00:08:23.120 --> 00:08:26.590
I tell you to do. Do

00:08:26.590 --> 00:08:26.600
not

00:08:26.600 --> 00:08:28.150
worry;

00:08:35.320 --> 00:08:37.550
they are not

00:08:37.560 --> 00:08:39.630
accountable

00:08:39.630 --> 00:08:39.640
for

00:08:39.640 --> 00:08:40.870
your

00:08:40.870 --> 00:08:40.880
call,

00:08:40.880 --> 00:08:43.950
you will stand before Me

00:08:43.960 --> 00:08:45.590
concerning what I've asked

00:08:45.600 --> 00:08:48.390
you to do.

00:08:48.400 --> 00:08:52.190
To be a parrot is dangerous. Similarities

00:08:52.190 --> 00:08:52.200
are

00:08:52.200 --> 00:08:56.030
okay,

00:08:58.240 --> 00:09:00.350
but the Lord said people may parrot

00:09:00.360 --> 00:09:03.750
you, but you are to stand alone.

00:09:03.760 --> 00:09:05.950
Say what I tell you with accuracy

00:09:05.960 --> 00:09:07.430
and boldness,

00:09:07.440 --> 00:09:09.910
with visions that I give you. You'll

00:09:09.920 --> 00:09:11.590
see it in the news,

00:09:11.600 --> 00:09:13.510
and your channel will grow well over a

00:09:13.520 --> 00:09:15.590
million in the days ahead.

00:09:15.600 --> 00:09:19.190
I'll use you for My end-time glory.

00:09:21.720 --> 00:09:24.829
It's not always easy to stand alone,

00:09:24.839 --> 00:09:27.190
but I say what He tells me to say.

00:09:27.200 --> 00:09:29.750
I know I can miss it;

00:09:29.760 --> 00:09:31.790
I'm just human.

00:09:33.720 --> 00:09:35.350
If I miss it, I'll be the first

00:09:35.350 --> 00:09:35.360
to

00:09:35.360 --> 00:09:37.110
tell you.

00:09:38.960 --> 00:09:42.110
I have no pride in it.

00:09:43.640 --> 00:09:45.070
You humble yourself

00:09:45.080 --> 00:09:46.990
and keep moving.

00:09:50.800 --> 00:09:52.510
Anybody who says they've never

00:09:52.520 --> 00:09:55.630
missed it is a liar.

00:09:55.640 --> 00:09:57.870
I see people miss it all the time. I

00:09:57.870 --> 00:09:57.880
meet

00:09:57.880 --> 00:09:59.950
people who say,

00:09:59.960 --> 00:10:01.190
'I don't ever miss it,

00:10:01.190 --> 00:10:01.200
Brandon.'It's

00:10:01.200 --> 00:10:03.470
called being human.

00:10:03.480 --> 00:10:04.950
I would love to meet some of the

00:10:04.960 --> 00:10:06.550
men in the Bible,

00:10:10.960 --> 00:10:13.030
like Isaiah

00:10:14.760 --> 00:10:16.670
and Jeremiah. They were awesome

00:10:16.680 --> 00:10:18.870
men of God, but we didn't see them

00:10:18.880 --> 00:10:21.870
as they were growing up

00:10:21.870 --> 00:10:21.880
or

00:10:21.880 --> 00:10:23.110
in

00:10:23.120 --> 00:10:24.990
their 20s. We don't have a glimpse of

00:10:25.000 --> 00:10:26.230
that.

00:10:26.240 --> 00:10:28.830
We know their strong points. We know the

00:10:28.830 --> 00:10:28.840
CliffNotes,

00:10:28.840 --> 00:10:31.230
the highlights.

00:10:31.240 --> 00:10:33.070
That's what the Bible tells us.

00:10:33.080 --> 00:10:34.870
It's like their

00:10:34.880 --> 00:10:36.710
Facebook highlight reel. I'm just being

00:10:36.720 --> 00:10:38.470
real with y'all. If they had a

00:10:38.480 --> 00:10:40.270
Facebook highlight reel, that's what

00:10:40.280 --> 00:10:41.590
we're reading.

00:10:41.600 --> 00:10:43.670
This is the best. Boom. And everybody's

00:10:43.680 --> 00:10:45.510
excited. But they don't see behind the

00:10:45.520 --> 00:10:47.230
scenes because Facebook doesn't show you that

00:10:47.240 --> 00:10:49.190
part, right? We don't know when people

00:10:49.190 --> 00:10:49.200
are

00:10:49.200 --> 00:10:50.590
having a bad day.

00:10:50.600 --> 00:10:51.950
We don't know their struggles. We don't

00:10:51.960 --> 00:10:53.829
know the depth of their

00:10:53.839 --> 00:10:55.829
relationship with the Lord because we

00:10:55.839 --> 00:10:57.950
didn't get to see that part. We got to

00:10:57.960 --> 00:11:00.030
see the highlight reel.

00:11:00.040 --> 00:11:01.390
And you can say that's blasphemous or

00:11:01.400 --> 00:11:03.710
whatever; it's the truth.

00:11:03.720 --> 00:11:06.030
We don't know everybody's

00:11:06.040 --> 00:11:07.590
flaws and everybody's stuff. You know

00:11:07.600 --> 00:11:09.790
why? Because we only see what the Lord

00:11:09.800 --> 00:11:11.510
allowed us to see. And through that

00:11:11.520 --> 00:11:15.110
passage of scripture,

00:11:15.120 --> 00:11:16.350
you don't know when they were down. You

00:11:16.360 --> 00:11:17.430
don't know what they went through in

00:11:17.440 --> 00:11:20.350
their marriages or their children or

00:11:20.360 --> 00:11:22.910
whatever.

00:11:22.920 --> 00:11:25.550
But everybody has a story.

00:11:25.560 --> 00:11:28.910
Everybody has a, b, c, d, and what

00:11:28.920 --> 00:11:31.030
you have from the day you were born

00:11:31.040 --> 00:11:32.910
to the day you die and what's in

00:11:32.920 --> 00:11:37.750
between the dashes.

00:11:37.760 --> 00:11:41.710
And so I separate myself

00:11:41.720 --> 00:11:44.270
as just a man.

00:11:44.280 --> 00:11:46.070
But as I pray

00:11:46.080 --> 00:11:48.310
and I tell you what I feel the Father

00:11:48.320 --> 00:11:51.230
has told me to tell you

00:11:51.230 --> 00:11:51.240
today—as

00:11:51.240 --> 00:11:53.390
I've prayed and interceded for

00:11:53.400 --> 00:11:54.790
America

00:11:54.800 --> 00:11:57.110
and what I see coming—I warned you

00:11:57.120 --> 00:11:59.070
what the Lord showed us concerning the

00:11:59.080 --> 00:12:00.870
economy

00:12:00.870 --> 00:12:00.880
and

00:12:00.880 --> 00:12:03.630
what I consider

00:12:03.640 --> 00:12:07.150
Trump's next plan.

00:12:07.160 --> 00:12:09.070
What did I tell you would

00:12:09.080 --> 00:12:11.830
happen if the Supreme Court

00:12:11.840 --> 00:12:15.550
ruled against him concerning

00:12:15.560 --> 00:12:18.510
the tariffs?

00:12:18.520 --> 00:12:21.590
I said he has a plan B.

00:12:21.600 --> 00:12:23.630
He's paddling as fast as he can in the

00:12:23.640 --> 00:12:25.910
canoe. Do you have the picture?

00:12:25.920 --> 00:12:28.150
Can you show them?

00:12:28.160 --> 00:12:31.270
He's paddling as fast as he can

00:12:31.280 --> 00:12:33.230
because I said he's trying to delay the

00:12:33.240 --> 00:12:34.750
inevitable.

00:12:34.760 --> 00:12:45.790
But in his mind,

00:12:45.790 --> 00:12:45.800
I

00:12:45.800 --> 00:12:49.190
said the economy is in trouble

00:12:49.200 --> 00:12:51.230
and there is no stopping this, right?

00:12:51.240 --> 00:12:52.710
Yeah. Say again. 32

00:12:52.710 --> 00:12:52.720
trillion.

00:12:52.720 --> 00:12:53.710
I don't know why when

00:12:53.710 --> 00:12:53.720
I switched

00:12:53.720 --> 00:12:55.310
back to it, it said

00:12:55.320 --> 00:12:57.190
32 million.

00:12:57.200 --> 00:12:58.110
