I saw them controlling that

00:38:19.360 --> 00:38:22.950
to try to help Russia.

00:38:30.000 --> 00:38:31.230
I said, 'That's where they're going to

00:38:31.240 --> 00:38:33.150
control

00:38:33.150 --> 00:38:33.160
Europe,'and

00:38:33.160 --> 00:38:34.670
you're going to see

00:38:34.670 --> 00:38:34.680
an

00:38:34.680 --> 00:38:37.150
escalation of things.

00:38:37.160 --> 00:38:39.990
As I keep praying,

00:38:42.640 --> 00:38:45.030
the Lord keeps downloading things to me

00:38:45.040 --> 00:38:47.710
about the economy, America,

00:38:47.710 --> 00:38:47.720
and

00:38:47.720 --> 00:38:50.150
the petrodollar.

00:38:50.160 --> 00:38:52.310
That's why I ask

00:38:52.320 --> 00:38:53.830
you all: do you really believe he's going

00:38:53.840 --> 00:38:55.390
to tell you when he's going to do it, or

00:38:55.400 --> 00:38:59.790
is that a tactic to

00:38:59.800 --> 00:39:01.990
get them to come to the table?

00:39:07.320 --> 00:39:08.630
They're not expecting it.

00:39:16.120 --> 00:39:18.430
It's about crippling the

00:39:18.440 --> 00:39:20.910
economy to the point where China doesn't

00:39:20.920 --> 00:39:23.590
buy oil from anyone else.

00:39:23.600 --> 00:39:26.510
Everybody has to come to America

00:39:26.510 --> 00:39:26.520
and

00:39:26.520 --> 00:39:29.270
our allies.

00:39:29.280 --> 00:39:32.590
This

00:39:32.600 --> 00:39:35.110
will be so strategic. Then the

00:39:35.120 --> 00:39:38.310
Lord said, 'Pray over

00:39:38.320 --> 00:39:39.790
Houston,

00:39:39.800 --> 00:39:44.230
Tuttle, and Louisiana.

00:39:44.240 --> 00:39:46.950
Pray over your main manufacturing plants

00:39:46.960 --> 00:39:48.590
in

00:39:48.590 --> 00:39:48.600
America—your

00:39:48.600 --> 00:39:52.910
grid, electric, water,

00:39:52.920 --> 00:39:55.830
and

00:39:55.840 --> 00:39:56.950
infrastructure.'I

00:39:56.960 --> 00:39:58.710
saw

00:39:58.720 --> 00:40:01.630
cities without power for up to three to

00:40:01.640 --> 00:40:05.590
four weeks—some

00:40:05.590 --> 00:40:05.600
longer—without

00:40:05.600 --> 00:40:07.950
any power in America in

00:40:07.960 --> 00:40:09.790
retaliation

00:40:09.800 --> 00:40:11.590
to what's happening over there. I

00:40:11.600 --> 00:40:14.190
said we have sleeper cells in

00:40:14.200 --> 00:40:17.030
our nation.

00:40:20.040 --> 00:40:21.390
It's putting it all together, telling

00:40:21.400 --> 00:40:24.150
you it's because the tariffs

00:40:24.160 --> 00:40:26.790
didn't happen like

00:40:26.800 --> 00:40:28.270
we wanted, and the Lord said

00:40:28.270 --> 00:40:28.280
to

00:40:28.280 --> 00:40:29.550
intercede for this. It was the valley

00:40:29.560 --> 00:40:34.630
of decision. Now it's all about a war of oil,

00:40:34.640 --> 00:40:38.230
trying to keep America as the top

00:40:38.240 --> 00:40:40.710
dog. He's a

00:40:40.720 --> 00:40:42.510
businessman.

00:40:42.520 --> 00:40:45.510
That's why I said pray for his mind

00:40:45.510 --> 00:40:45.520
and

00:40:45.520 --> 00:40:47.950
the way he's

00:40:47.950 --> 00:40:47.960
thinking—the

00:40:47.960 --> 00:40:49.910
instructions he's getting from

00:40:49.920 --> 00:40:53.230
people outside of his circle,

00:40:53.240 --> 00:40:56.590
taking counsel from the ungodly

00:40:56.590 --> 00:40:56.600
and

00:40:56.600 --> 00:40:58.670
being pressured. And the Lord said

00:40:58.680 --> 00:41:00.990
to pray against those

00:41:00.990 --> 00:41:01.000
with

00:41:01.000 --> 00:41:03.110
an Ivy League education. Does

00:41:03.120 --> 00:41:04.790
anybody remember that? Because we came

00:41:04.800 --> 00:41:06.510
against that one night,

00:41:06.520 --> 00:41:08.550
and we prayed against the Ivy League

00:41:08.560 --> 00:41:10.350
education. I said it's because they have

00:41:10.360 --> 00:41:14.030
corrupt communication. Harvard,

00:41:14.040 --> 00:41:18.110
Princeton, Yale—all these Ivy League

00:41:18.120 --> 00:41:20.510
students

00:41:21.720 --> 00:41:24.430
have a reprobate mind because they've

00:41:24.440 --> 00:41:28.590
been educated by people who believe in

00:41:28.600 --> 00:41:31.150
stupid theology that is

00:41:31.150 --> 00:41:31.160
off-base from

00:41:31.160 --> 00:41:33.470
even what the Bible says.

00:41:33.480 --> 00:41:34.350
And that's why I brought out the

00:41:34.360 --> 00:41:37.270
scripture: 'These are unlearned

00:41:37.270 --> 00:41:37.280
men.'They

00:41:37.280 --> 00:41:39.470
marveled because they had been with

00:41:39.480 --> 00:41:41.230
Jesus.

00:41:41.240 --> 00:41:44.030
They knew they had been with Jesus. And

00:41:44.040 --> 00:41:46.910
I said the key to walking in these

00:41:46.920 --> 00:41:50.310
last days and having the mind of Christ

00:41:50.320 --> 00:41:53.110
is being with Jesus.

00:41:53.120 --> 00:41:56.190
You will have wisdom beyond

00:41:56.190 --> 00:41:56.200
anyone's,

00:41:56.200 --> 00:41:58.710
beyond your years, because you

00:41:58.720 --> 00:42:01.070
have been endowed with the Holy Ghost

00:42:01.080 --> 00:42:04.190
and fire. And He has given you wisdom on

00:42:04.200 --> 00:42:07.270
how to lead in these last days.

00:42:07.280 --> 00:42:11.070
You have to spend time with Him

00:42:11.080 --> 00:42:13.430
because you've been with Jesus.

00:42:13.440 --> 00:42:15.390
No matter if you say, 'Well, Brandon,

00:42:15.400 --> 00:42:17.390
I'm so thankful that

00:42:17.400 --> 00:42:18.590
you're here,'or

00:42:18.590 --> 00:42:18.600
whatever—no,

00:42:18.600 --> 00:42:21.430
you have the same ability to hear

00:42:21.440 --> 00:42:24.350
God.

00:42:24.360 --> 00:42:26.670
You're wall-to-wall Holy Ghost. What

00:42:26.680 --> 00:42:28.070
does it take?

00:42:28.080 --> 00:42:31.030
Being with Jesus.

00:42:31.040 --> 00:42:33.150
Then when they saw the boldness of

00:42:33.160 --> 00:42:36.070
Peter and John and perceived that they

00:42:36.080 --> 00:42:38.270
were unlearned

00:42:38.280 --> 00:42:40.950
and ignorant men,

00:42:40.960 --> 00:42:44.190
they marveled and they took knowledge

00:42:44.200 --> 00:42:48.110
of them that they had been with

00:42:48.110 --> 00:42:48.120
Jesus—Acts

00:42:48.120 --> 00:42:50.470
4:13.

00:42:50.480 --> 00:42:51.870
One of my favorites right there.

00:42:51.880 --> 00:42:53.390
I should memorize

00:42:53.400 --> 00:42:54.950
that

00:42:54.960 --> 00:42:57.190
because it's the whole key.

00:42:57.200 --> 00:42:58.910
That's the whole key to your foundation

00:42:58.920 --> 00:43:02.030
of who you are: being with Jesus,

00:43:02.040 --> 00:43:04.230
reading your Bible, and praying every

00:43:04.240 --> 00:43:07.550
day. And I don't care if you

00:43:07.550 --> 00:43:07.560
have

00:43:07.560 --> 00:43:11.030
just a 12th-grade education or whatever.

00:43:11.040 --> 00:43:12.910
You could just be some backwoods person

00:43:12.920 --> 00:43:14.790
and be like, 'I

00:43:14.790 --> 00:43:14.800
know

00:43:14.800 --> 00:43:16.190
hardly anything; I didn't hardly

00:43:16.200 --> 00:43:17.830
pay attention in school; I was drunk half the

00:43:17.830 --> 00:43:17.840
time,'or

00:43:17.840 --> 00:43:19.510
whatever. I don't know.

00:43:19.520 --> 00:43:22.230
But you just know who you are now

00:43:22.230 --> 00:43:22.240
as

00:43:22.240 --> 00:43:24.870
a new creation created in Christ

00:43:24.880 --> 00:43:27.350
Jesus. I'm a new creature.

00:43:27.360 --> 00:43:29.990
Behold, all the old has passed away;

00:43:30.000 --> 00:43:31.990
behold, all things have become new. Who

00:43:32.000 --> 00:43:36.150
are you? I have been with Jesus.

00:43:36.160 --> 00:43:38.230
And you'll get things by the Spirit of

00:43:38.240 --> 00:43:40.990
the Lord that these Ivy

00:43:40.990 --> 00:43:41.000
League-educated

00:43:41.000 --> 00:43:43.670
people won't have any clue about because

00:43:43.680 --> 00:43:44.990
you have been with

00:43:44.990 --> 00:43:45.000
Him.

00:43:45.000 --> 00:43:46.830
And the Lord said today when I was

00:43:46.840 --> 00:43:50.230
driving to get my mail, He said to me,

00:43:50.240 --> 00:43:52.030
'Brandon, I want you to pray over the

00:43:52.040 --> 00:43:53.270
worship,

00:43:53.280 --> 00:43:56.230
for great worship songs are coming to

00:43:56.240 --> 00:44:00.230
the ones that have been with Me.

00:44:00.240 --> 00:44:03.590
I'm going to give the worship now.

00:44:03.600 --> 00:44:06.590
I'm ready to release the new music that

00:44:06.600 --> 00:44:09.030
the world has never seen before. I'm

00:44:09.040 --> 00:44:11.430
ready to release the worship that will

00:44:11.440 --> 00:44:14.630
break

00:44:14.630 --> 00:44:14.640
charts—not

00:44:14.640 --> 00:44:17.390
for a Dove Award, not for a Grammy,

00:44:17.400 --> 00:44:20.710
not for whatever. I'm doing it because I want

00:44:20.720 --> 00:44:24.470
to bring worship into the church

00:44:24.480 --> 00:44:27.470
to bring down the glory,

00:44:27.480 --> 00:44:29.790
to fill the atmosphere full of the

00:44:29.790 --> 00:44:29.800
glory.'But

00:44:29.800 --> 00:44:32.830
the Lord said, 'There's new

00:44:32.840 --> 00:44:35.990
sounds coming.'I want you to hear that.

00:44:36.000 --> 00:44:37.630
He said it to me, 'Jesus, I'm bringing

00:44:37.640 --> 00:44:39.190
new sounds that have never been heard

00:44:39.200 --> 00:44:42.070
before. I'm bringing worship and songs

00:44:42.080 --> 00:44:44.070
that have never been sung

00:44:44.070 --> 00:44:44.080
before.'This

00:44:44.080 --> 00:44:45.870
is going to be heavenly worship that's

00:44:45.880 --> 00:44:46.950
about to

00:44:46.950 --> 00:44:46.960
influence

00:44:46.960 --> 00:44:49.790
the earth.

00:44:49.800 --> 00:44:53.390
Do you have your antenna up to catch it?

00:44:53.400 --> 00:44:56.110
Bring the scripture back.

00:44:56.120 --> 00:44:58.670
Now, when they saw

00:44:58.680 --> 00:45:00.590
the boldness—how do you know when

00:45:00.600 --> 00:45:02.750
the Spirit of the Lord is coming on you?

00:45:02.750 --> 00:45:02.760
Because

00:45:02.760 --> 00:45:04.510
you're bold.

00:45:04.520 --> 00:45:07.310
They saw boldness on them.

00:45:07.320 --> 00:45:08.910
What did they see? You have to look

00:45:08.920 --> 00:45:13.150
at what was the fruit of the root

00:45:13.160 --> 00:45:15.070
of being with Jesus. What was the fruit

00:45:15.080 --> 00:45:18.030
of the root? Now when they saw the

00:45:18.040 --> 00:45:21.750
boldness of Peter and John,

00:45:21.760 --> 00:45:23.430
they knew right then: these guys are

00:45:23.440 --> 00:45:25.150
bold.

00:45:25.160 --> 00:45:27.710
They perceived they were unlearned. They

00:45:27.710 --> 00:45:27.720
were

00:45:27.720 --> 00:45:28.830
like, 'These guys

00:45:28.840 --> 00:45:30.510
aren't that smart,'and

00:45:30.510 --> 00:45:30.520
that

00:45:30.520 --> 00:45:32.950
they

00:45:32.950 --> 00:45:32.960
were

00:45:32.960 --> 00:45:34.830
ignorant

00:45:34.830 --> 00:45:34.840
men.

00:45:34.840 --> 00:45:36.950
They marveled; they were

00:45:36.950 --> 00:45:36.960
in

00:45:36.960 --> 00:45:38.150
shock

00:45:38.150 --> 00:45:38.160
and

00:45:38.160 --> 00:45:40.030
awe,

00:45:40.030 --> 00:45:40.040
and

00:45:40.040 --> 00:45:41.910
they took knowledge of them and

00:45:41.920 --> 00:45:43.150
they took knowledge of Him. They

00:45:43.160 --> 00:45:44.830
were so smart and had so much Holy

00:45:44.840 --> 00:45:51.150
Ghost on them that they were taking notes.

00:45:51.160 --> 00:45:54.830
They had been with Jesus.

00:45:54.840 --> 00:45:58.870
You can be with Jesus, too.

00:45:58.880 --> 00:46:01.150
I look for Him when He talks about

00:46:01.160 --> 00:46:02.750
sports;

00:46:02.750 --> 00:46:02.760
He

00:46:02.760 --> 00:46:03.790
tells me who's going to win the

00:46:03.800 --> 00:46:06.510
championship this year.

00:46:06.520 --> 00:46:09.150
We talk about it all the time.

00:46:09.160 --> 00:46:10.830
He knows the things that I like to talk

00:46:10.840 --> 00:46:13.630
about and we're friends.

00:46:13.640 --> 00:46:15.630
I love basketball. He told me who was

00:46:15.640 --> 00:46:17.310
going to win the championship last

00:46:17.320 --> 00:46:19.350
night. He talked about it—I didn't tell

00:46:19.360 --> 00:46:21.310
anybody—He

00:46:21.320 --> 00:46:24.510
tells me things like that.

00:46:24.520 --> 00:46:27.390
We talk about stuff. He tells me

00:46:27.400 --> 00:46:29.710
who's going to win the NBA championship

00:46:29.720 --> 00:46:31.710
way before. He already told me

00:46:31.710 --> 00:46:31.720
a

00:46:31.720 --> 00:46:33.990
couple of weeks ago.

00:46:34.000 --> 00:46:35.110
He'll talk about it and say, 'Hey, this

00:46:35.120 --> 00:46:37.670
is who's going to be in the

00:46:37.670 --> 00:46:37.680
finals.'He

00:46:37.680 --> 00:46:38.750
goes, 'You know, it's going to be a

00:46:38.760 --> 00:46:40.550
good

00:46:41.830 --> 00:46:41.840
game.'Wow,

00:46:43.000 --> 00:46:45.070
I'm excited to watch it. He

00:46:45.070 --> 00:46:45.080
says,

00:46:45.080 --> 00:46:47.390
'Don't tell me anymore;

00:46:47.400 --> 00:46:48.870
I want to know

00:46:48.870 --> 00:46:48.880
before.'That

00:46:48.880 --> 00:46:52.710
kind of gives me a roundabout,

00:46:52.720 --> 00:46:54.990
but we just talk about things because

00:46:54.990 --> 00:46:55.000
I

00:46:55.000 --> 00:46:58.990
have been with Him; He's my friend

00:46:59.000 --> 00:47:02.150
and friends talk about things.

00:47:02.160 --> 00:47:04.950
Like I said, I look at Him more

00:47:04.960 --> 00:47:06.870
as a companion, and even if this channel

00:47:06.880 --> 00:47:08.670
or anything else goes away, I'm just

00:47:08.680 --> 00:47:10.150
going to sail off, in a sense, and just

00:47:10.160 --> 00:47:13.230
be friends with Him. I could care less.

00:47:13.240 --> 00:47:15.110
I just look at Him

00:47:15.120 --> 00:47:17.110
because I want people to say they

00:47:17.120 --> 00:47:19.670
marvel because Brandon has been with

00:47:19.680 --> 00:47:21.990
Jesus. Not because Brandon is anything

00:47:22.000 --> 00:47:26.230
special, but because Jesus is in me.

00:47:26.240 --> 00:47:30.150
I want people to see it;

00:47:30.160 --> 00:47:33.470
I want them to get it themselves.

00:47:33.480 --> 00:47:36.670
He's no respecter of persons.

00:47:36.680 --> 00:47:38.990
You may be the best quilt maker out

00:47:39.000 --> 00:47:40.310
there and He'll teach you a different

00:47:40.320 --> 00:47:42.350
way to make a better quilt.

00:47:42.360 --> 00:47:45.470
You could be the best

00:47:45.470 --> 00:47:45.480
cowboy.

00:47:45.480 --> 00:47:47.590
You say, 'Well, I work with cows; I

00:47:47.600 --> 00:47:49.310
work with pigs; I work with

00:47:49.310 --> 00:47:49.320
whatever.'I

00:47:49.320 --> 00:47:50.910
know we're

00:47:50.910 --> 00:47:50.920
not

00:47:50.920 --> 00:47:52.470
supposed to eat pork,

00:47:52.480 --> 00:47:53.430
but

00:47:53.440 --> 00:47:55.190
it's

00:47:55.190 --> 00:47:55.200
interesting—He'll

00:47:55.200 --> 00:47:57.350
talk to you about chickens.

00:47:57.360 --> 00:47:58.670
He'll talk to you about sheep. He'll

00:47:58.680 --> 00:47:59.750
talk about,

00:47:59.760 --> 00:48:01.670
'Hey, if you plant this over here a

00:48:01.680 --> 00:48:03.390
little bit different, that'll grow

00:48:03.400 --> 00:48:05.030
better because that soil is a little bit...

00:48:05.040 --> 00:48:07.630
it's only 10 feet away,

00:48:07.640 --> 00:48:11.550
but that right there is a good spot.

00:48:11.560 --> 00:48:15.910
If you plant that right there,

00:48:15.920 --> 00:48:18.270
it'll grow

00:48:18.270 --> 00:48:18.280
better.'It

00:48:18.280 --> 00:48:19.790
doesn't

00:48:19.800 --> 00:48:21.910
matter.

00:48:21.920 --> 00:48:24.550
Practice His presence.

00:48:24.560 --> 00:48:26.630
Whatever He tells you to do, do it and

00:48:26.640 --> 00:48:27.990
you'll be blessed.

00:48:28.000 --> 00:48:29.830
People get ticked off at me all the time

00:48:29.830 --> 00:48:29.840
because

00:48:29.840 --> 00:48:32.470
He tells me investments.

00:48:32.480 --> 00:48:33.390
He does.

00:48:33.400 --> 00:48:35.230
And people get mad when they see I get

00:48:35.240 --> 00:48:37.750
blessed.

00:48:37.760 --> 00:48:40.310
But if you are with Jesus, He'll tell you

00:48:40.320 --> 00:48:41.630
things.

00:48:41.640 --> 00:48:42.950
So don't get mad at me when I get

00:48:42.960 --> 00:48:44.830
blessed.

00:48:44.840 --> 00:48:46.270
I talk about it all the time to my

00:48:46.280 --> 00:48:47.230
family.

00:48:47.240 --> 00:48:48.190
I said, 'Listen, this is what the Lord

00:48:48.200 --> 00:48:50.830
said to do.'And do you know

00:48:50.840 --> 00:48:52.550
I've tried to obey Him every single

00:48:52.560 --> 00:48:54.430
step of the way? Even

00:48:54.430 --> 00:48:54.440
when

00:48:54.440 --> 00:48:57.390
people go, 'Well,

00:48:57.400 --> 00:48:58.790
who are you?'Do you know I used to

00:48:58.800 --> 00:49:00.310
stand in front of some of the biggest

00:49:00.320 --> 00:49:02.350
businessmen in all

00:49:02.360 --> 00:49:03.950
of a place

00:49:03.960 --> 00:49:05.910
and they would ask me questions?

00:49:05.910 --> 00:49:05.920
Now,

00:49:05.920 --> 00:49:08.190
do I have everything always down?

00:49:08.200 --> 00:49:09.830
But people can see when you've been with

00:49:09.840 --> 00:49:11.670
Jesus.

00:49:11.680 --> 00:49:14.590
I know I can miss it,

00:49:14.600 --> 00:49:17.110
but I just marvel because He has a

00:49:17.120 --> 00:49:19.190
topic about everything.

00:49:19.200 --> 00:49:20.710
He'll talk about the birds, the flowers, He'll talk...

00:49:23.120 --> 00:49:27.590
I love my flowers,

00:49:27.600 --> 00:49:29.270
ferns, and

00:49:29.280 --> 00:49:31.270
greenery.

00:49:31.280 --> 00:49:34.110
I'll spend hours just being quiet,

00:49:34.120 --> 00:49:36.790
and I teach my little girl, Paisley;

00:49:36.790 --> 00:49:36.800
she'll

00:49:36.800 --> 00:49:39.590
come up beside me and I say, 'Listen,

00:49:39.600 --> 00:49:41.750
if you're going to be in this zone, this

00:49:41.760 --> 00:49:43.550
is where we don't talk.

00:49:43.560 --> 00:49:45.350
This is where we listen.'And I teach

00:49:45.360 --> 00:49:46.790
her to listen. This

00:49:46.790 --> 00:49:46.800
is

00:49:46.800 --> 00:49:48.470
not where we talk. I spend time

00:49:48.470 --> 00:49:48.480
in

00:49:48.480 --> 00:49:51.030
quiet. You have to be quiet. God

00:49:51.030 --> 00:49:51.040
is

00:49:51.040 --> 00:49:53.550
not going to compete with you.

00:49:53.560 --> 00:49:56.510
He's not going to try to overpower you.

00:49:56.520 --> 00:49:58.110
He's a gentleman,

00:49:58.120 --> 00:49:59.990
but if you're always running your mouth,

00:50:00.000 --> 00:50:02.630
He's not going to talk. Shh.

00:50:02.640 --> 00:50:05.030
Be still when you're outside.

00:50:05.040 --> 00:50:07.710
He'll talk to you. And I always make an

00:50:07.720 --> 00:50:10.310
atmosphere for Him to speak to me.

00:50:10.320 --> 00:50:12.070
And I'll pray in the Spirit. Just pray

00:50:12.080 --> 00:50:13.590
softly. You don't have to be yelling in

00:50:13.600 --> 00:50:15.910
tongues with everybody

00:50:15.920 --> 00:50:17.310
in the neighborhood looking at you

00:50:17.320 --> 00:50:19.630
going, 'What is going on with that

00:50:19.640 --> 00:50:20.910
dude?'I

00:50:20.920 --> 00:50:24.190
just pray softly to myself. Worship.

00:50:24.200 --> 00:50:27.030
Worship. Thank You, Jesus. I try to

00:50:27.040 --> 00:50:29.430
continually stay in the flow of the

00:50:29.440 --> 00:50:30.990
river

00:50:31.000 --> 00:50:33.830
because I told Diana it's always

00:50:33.840 --> 00:50:36.270
flowing.

00:50:36.280 --> 00:50:39.390
He's always talking.

00:50:39.400 --> 00:50:42.630
The Holy Spirit is always talking to you

00:50:42.640 --> 00:50:46.430
and leading you. There's no end to it

00:50:46.440 --> 00:50:50.430
if you are sensitive to it.

00:50:50.440 --> 00:50:53.390
He'll tell you everything.

00:50:53.400 --> 00:50:55.430
All that you say in

00:50:55.440 --> 00:50:57.150
word and deed, we give all to the glory

00:50:57.160 --> 00:50:59.230
of God. I even talked to Pastor Chip. He

00:50:59.230 --> 00:50:59.240
said,

00:50:59.240 --> 00:51:00.790
"You know, Brandon, he'll even tell

00:51:00.800 --> 00:51:03.390
you about sports."I said, "Yes,

00:51:03.400 --> 00:51:07.270
he does. He talks about sports,

00:51:07.270 --> 00:51:07.280
Pastor."And

00:51:07.280 --> 00:51:10.030
he, Pastor Chip, is a coach at

00:51:10.040 --> 00:51:12.630
heart, Champions for Christ. He's all

00:51:12.640 --> 00:51:13.710
into it,

00:51:13.720 --> 00:51:15.710
and he loves to talk about sports. He

00:51:15.720 --> 00:51:18.430
loves baseball. He loves

00:51:18.440 --> 00:51:20.190
things like that, you know,

00:51:20.200 --> 00:51:23.550
football. He loves the Chicago Bears. And

00:51:23.560 --> 00:51:25.070
the Lord will sit down and

00:51:25.080 --> 00:51:28.070
just listen and talk about things:

00:51:28.080 --> 00:51:30.670
"How do you become

00:51:30.670 --> 00:51:30.680
better?"He

00:51:30.680 --> 00:51:32.510
wants you to be a champion on every

00:51:32.520 --> 00:51:35.470
single level of your

00:51:35.470 --> 00:51:35.480
life—to

00:51:35.480 --> 00:51:37.910
be the head and not the tail, above

00:51:37.920 --> 00:51:40.390
and not beneath. But we have made him into

00:51:40.400 --> 00:51:43.190
some kind of religious figure that we

00:51:43.200 --> 00:51:46.070
can't talk to.

00:51:46.080 --> 00:51:48.350
And God is an ever-present help

00:51:48.360 --> 00:51:50.710
in a time of need. And guess what?

00:51:50.720 --> 00:51:52.710
I'm always in need

00:51:52.720 --> 00:51:56.270
of him.

00:51:56.280 --> 00:51:59.790
I don't think I ever don't need him. Do you? Do you not need him?

00:52:04.440 --> 00:52:06.030
If you don't,

00:52:06.040 --> 00:52:08.910
you're in trouble.

00:52:08.920 --> 00:52:11.030
He's an ever-present help in a time of

00:52:11.040 --> 00:52:16.230
need. I'm always in need of him.

00:52:16.240 --> 00:52:18.390
I don't care who you are; I need him in

00:52:18.400 --> 00:52:19.750
everything.

00:52:19.760 --> 00:52:23.350
Tell me,

00:52:23.360 --> 00:52:26.270
teach me how to drive my car better

00:52:26.280 --> 00:52:29.230
to get better gas mileage.

00:52:29.240 --> 00:52:31.910
Teach me when I'm going down,

00:52:31.920 --> 00:52:33.510
and he'll say, "You know, you didn't

00:52:33.520 --> 00:52:34.550
handle that real well."He just

00:52:34.560 --> 00:52:35.750
corrected me even on how I was cranky

00:52:35.750 --> 00:52:35.760
with

00:52:35.760 --> 00:52:37.630
Braden just a second ago. He said, "You owe an apology. Oh, you

00:52:37.640 --> 00:52:38.990
owe him an

00:52:38.990 --> 00:52:39.000
apology."I'm

00:52:39.000 --> 00:52:40.910
sorry,

00:52:40.920 --> 00:52:42.830
Braden; I shouldn't be so cranky. It's

00:52:42.840 --> 00:52:43.830
the truth.

00:52:43.840 --> 00:52:46.190
He corrects me all the time, but he's

00:52:46.200 --> 00:52:48.030
always tugging my heart: "You need to be

00:52:48.040 --> 00:52:50.990
more kind. You need to be more patient.

00:52:51.000 --> 00:52:53.270
You need to walk in

00:52:54.470 --> 00:52:54.480
love."I'm

00:52:56.040 --> 00:52:58.990
always wanting to incline

00:52:59.000 --> 00:53:02.550
my ear to him

00:53:02.560 --> 00:53:05.030
so that my kids learn to operate the

00:53:05.040 --> 00:53:06.670
same way.

00:53:06.680 --> 00:53:08.230
And you know what? He has an opinion

00:53:08.240 --> 00:53:12.910
about everybody I talk to.

00:53:12.920 --> 00:53:14.310
There's some people I get off the phone

00:53:14.320 --> 00:53:17.590
with and he says, "They're in trouble.

00:53:17.600 --> 00:53:19.790
They won't make it

00:53:19.800 --> 00:53:21.150
because they're not doing this and this

00:53:21.160 --> 00:53:22.430
and

00:53:22.430 --> 00:53:22.440
this."I

00:53:22.440 --> 00:53:23.550
said, "Well, what do

00:53:23.550 --> 00:53:23.560
you—it's

00:53:23.560 --> 00:53:26.030
none of your business.

00:53:26.040 --> 00:53:29.470
They didn't ask for your advice.

00:53:29.480 --> 00:53:30.990
They didn't ask for your advice. And if

00:53:31.000 --> 00:53:33.790
you gave them your advice,

00:53:33.800 --> 00:53:35.990
it's not them getting it from me;

00:53:36.000 --> 00:53:37.510
it's getting it from you."There's so

00:53:37.520 --> 00:53:38.870
much correction about it. But he always

00:53:38.880 --> 00:53:41.430
has an opinion about everything.

00:53:41.440 --> 00:53:44.070
And I love how he talks about

00:53:44.080 --> 00:53:45.630
Billy Burke.

00:53:45.640 --> 00:53:48.710
I know, y'all, every time I talk to

00:53:48.710 --> 00:53:48.720
the Lord—that's

00:53:48.720 --> 00:53:53.070
my

00:53:53.070 --> 00:53:53.080
friend—and

00:53:53.080 --> 00:53:55.510
I am not a person who brown-noses.

00:53:55.520 --> 00:53:57.070
I tell you that; I'm just telling you the

00:53:57.080 --> 00:53:59.510
flat truth.

00:53:59.520 --> 00:54:02.150
He'll say, "That's my friend."This

00:54:02.150 --> 00:54:02.160
is what

00:54:02.160 --> 00:54:04.150
this is, and the way he

00:54:04.160 --> 00:54:07.190
instructs about certain people.

00:54:07.200 --> 00:54:08.830
If he ever says—and there's times he

00:54:08.830 --> 00:54:08.840
has—"I

00:54:08.840 --> 00:54:11.590
don't know them.

00:54:11.600 --> 00:54:13.750
I don't know them.

00:54:13.760 --> 00:54:15.710
What they're saying is a lie.

00:54:15.720 --> 00:54:18.150
They're fake.

00:54:18.160 --> 00:54:19.630
They're two-faced.

00:54:19.640 --> 00:54:22.390
They're not all in for me.

00:54:22.400 --> 00:54:24.430
Be cautious of

00:54:24.430 --> 00:54:24.440
them."And

00:54:24.440 --> 00:54:26.270
he'll say certain things to me,

00:54:26.280 --> 00:54:27.790
warning me,

00:54:27.800 --> 00:54:29.150
"Protect yourself against that

00:54:29.160 --> 00:54:31.430
individual. Don't allow him in too

00:54:33.750 --> 00:54:33.760
close."What

00:54:34.840 --> 00:54:38.710
does he say about you?

00:54:38.720 --> 00:54:40.590
Are you thinking you're hiding something

00:54:40.600 --> 00:54:44.230
from him?

00:54:44.240 --> 00:54:45.710
When you're trying to hide stuff from

00:54:45.720 --> 00:54:47.230
everybody else,

00:54:47.240 --> 00:54:50.910
maybe they can't see it, but he can.

00:54:50.920 --> 00:54:53.670
What do you display in the spirit realm

00:54:53.680 --> 00:54:55.550
and your fragrance? What is your

00:54:55.560 --> 00:54:57.630
fragrance?

00:54:57.640 --> 00:55:02.310
Do you stink?

00:55:02.320 --> 00:55:03.950
And the only way we're upright and the

00:55:03.960 --> 00:55:06.230
only way we're able to be right is

00:55:06.230 --> 00:55:06.240
by

00:55:06.240 --> 00:55:07.750
always being underneath that

00:55:07.760 --> 00:55:09.030
blood.

00:55:09.040 --> 00:55:12.070
I take communion all the time. And I

00:55:12.080 --> 00:55:15.470
know God, I can't do this on my own.

00:55:15.480 --> 00:55:16.750
So if he's warning

00:55:16.750 --> 00:55:16.760
him

00:55:16.760 --> 00:55:17.950
about me and somebody said, "Well,

00:55:17.950 --> 00:55:17.960
Brandon,

00:55:17.960 --> 00:55:19.030
this is what we say about

00:55:19.030 --> 00:55:19.040
you."I'm

00:55:19.040 --> 00:55:20.870
not here to lie to

00:55:20.880 --> 00:55:22.430
you. I know I realize I've got

00:55:22.430 --> 00:55:22.440
something

00:55:22.440 --> 00:55:23.830
I'm going

00:55:23.840 --> 00:55:26.430
through.

00:55:26.440 --> 00:55:29.190
But I ask him to search me and know me:

00:55:29.200 --> 00:55:31.910
"Create in me a clean heart.

00:55:31.920 --> 00:55:34.230
Fix it.

00:55:34.230 --> 00:55:34.240
Fix

00:55:34.240 --> 00:55:36.390
it."But

00:55:36.400 --> 00:55:38.790
I want when I get done that

00:55:38.800 --> 00:55:41.710
just like they marveled.

00:55:41.720 --> 00:55:44.470
They marveled because they had been with

00:55:44.480 --> 00:55:47.470
Jesus.

00:55:47.480 --> 00:55:49.390
Do people marvel

00:55:49.400 --> 00:55:51.270
after you leave because you have been

00:55:51.280 --> 00:55:54.830
with Jesus?

00:55:54.840 --> 00:55:56.710
Or do they say, "Man, she is a Sister

00:55:56.720 --> 00:55:58.990
Clipboard. Woo,

00:55:59.000 --> 00:56:00.950
that girl right there has a Jezebel

00:56:00.960 --> 00:56:02.670
spirit.

00:56:02.680 --> 00:56:05.390
Does she have a Delilah spirit? Does

00:56:05.400 --> 00:56:09.110
she have, or does he have some kind

00:56:09.110 --> 00:56:09.120
of—I

00:56:09.120 --> 00:56:10.510
have to go and take a bath."I feel

00:56:10.520 --> 00:56:11.830
nothing,

00:56:11.840 --> 00:56:13.590
and I can walk up to a sweet old lady in

00:56:13.600 --> 00:56:16.990
the back row and she has presence.

00:56:17.000 --> 00:56:19.470
She's just an intercessor in the church,

00:56:19.470 --> 00:56:19.480
a

00:56:19.480 --> 00:56:21.030
sweet little black lady. He told

00:56:21.040 --> 00:56:23.310
me about a sweet little black lady; she

00:56:23.320 --> 00:56:25.110
walked to him and he said, "My goodness,

00:56:25.120 --> 00:56:26.750
lady, you have

00:56:26.750 --> 00:56:26.760
it."You

00:56:26.760 --> 00:56:28.750
know why? Because presence knows

00:56:28.760 --> 00:56:33.310
presence.

00:56:33.320 --> 00:56:35.550
Does it make sense what I'm saying?

00:56:35.560 --> 00:56:37.910
Is it okay?

00:56:43.160 --> 00:56:46.030
Presence knows presence.

00:56:46.040 --> 00:56:47.550
And that sweet little black lady on the

00:56:47.560 --> 00:56:49.910
back row of this

00:56:49.910 --> 00:56:49.920
building—his

00:56:49.920 --> 00:56:52.150
meeting he was

00:56:52.150 --> 00:56:52.160
holding—he

00:56:52.160 --> 00:56:53.710
walked up to this woman and he

00:56:53.720 --> 00:56:55.230
grabbed a hold of her hand. And the

00:56:55.240 --> 00:56:57.750
moment he grabbed her hand, there was

00:56:57.760 --> 00:56:59.750
impartation

00:56:59.760 --> 00:57:01.910
because what she was carrying was what

00:57:01.920 --> 00:57:04.150
he was carrying. And iron sharpens

00:57:04.160 --> 00:57:06.350
iron. But you can always tell when

00:57:06.360 --> 00:57:08.430
somebody's been with Jesus. And

00:57:08.440 --> 00:57:10.670
this was just a little old

00:57:10.680 --> 00:57:13.950
lady.

00:57:13.960 --> 00:57:15.590
It wasn't the big preacher on the front

00:57:15.600 --> 00:57:16.910
row.

00:57:16.920 --> 00:57:19.270
It was a little old lady.

00:57:19.280 --> 00:57:21.670
She had been with Jesus.

00:57:21.680 --> 00:57:24.070
And you can marvel at it. So I don't

00:57:24.080 --> 00:57:25.750
care if you're sitting on the back row

00:57:25.760 --> 00:57:28.990
or the front row or in between.

00:57:29.000 --> 00:57:32.630
Fragrance and presence follows you.

00:57:32.640 --> 00:57:37.110
When you stay with Jesus,

00:57:37.120 --> 00:57:38.870
there's no pretending.

00:57:38.880 --> 00:57:41.550
You can't pray at it.

00:57:41.560 --> 00:57:43.630
It is a fragrance

00:57:43.640 --> 00:57:46.750
and it is a taste.

00:57:46.760 --> 00:57:51.910
What does your fruit taste like?

00:57:51.920 --> 00:57:53.470
What do you—"Taste and see that

00:57:53.480 --> 00:57:55.230
the Lord is good"—but what do people

00:57:55.240 --> 00:57:59.030
taste when they're around you?

00:57:59.040 --> 00:58:01.750
Insecurity, pride, jealousy,

00:58:01.760 --> 00:58:04.190
bitterness, anger,

00:58:04.190 --> 00:58:04.200
or

00:58:04.200 --> 00:58:06.270
all the fruits of the Spirit? What do

00:58:06.280 --> 00:58:09.070
they taste when they're around you? What

00:58:09.080 --> 00:58:11.270
fragrance do you bring when

00:58:11.280 --> 00:58:13.270
you walk in a room? You can tell when

00:58:13.280 --> 00:58:15.670
there's strife in a room.

00:58:15.680 --> 00:58:17.430
When you're bickering with your

00:58:17.440 --> 00:58:19.270
wife and you come in a room, you

00:58:19.280 --> 00:58:21.790
can tell when an atmosphere is charged

00:58:21.800 --> 00:58:23.510
with anger. You can go, "There's

00:58:23.520 --> 00:58:25.950
something bad been up in here.

00:58:25.960 --> 00:58:27.910
Something's going on."I can walk into a

00:58:27.920 --> 00:58:30.030
house that I'm looking at and I can

00:58:30.040 --> 00:58:31.750
feel critters,

00:58:31.760 --> 00:58:33.670
and I can feel them push on you

00:58:33.680 --> 00:58:35.870
and I say, "Uh, there's devils in this

00:58:35.880 --> 00:58:38.190
house."They

00:58:38.200 --> 00:58:41.590
know when I'm there.

00:58:41.600 --> 00:58:42.790
But

00:58:42.800 --> 00:58:44.750
when I walk in a house and you feel

00:58:44.760 --> 00:58:46.510
the presence

00:58:46.520 --> 00:58:49.790
and you go, "There's such a sweet

00:58:49.800 --> 00:58:51.510
fragrance."We

00:58:51.520 --> 00:58:54.150
had an individual come by and

00:58:54.160 --> 00:58:55.590
eat dinner with us

00:58:55.600 --> 00:58:57.670
and they sat on the couch and they

00:58:57.680 --> 00:59:00.350
fell asleep.

00:59:00.360 --> 00:59:04.270
I try very hard to keep strife out.

00:59:04.280 --> 00:59:06.910
You let that fragrance and

00:59:06.920 --> 00:59:09.030
even when I say, "What do you feel when

00:59:09.040 --> 00:59:11.030
you come to my house?

00:59:11.040 --> 00:59:12.550
What do you feel when you go to somebody

00:59:12.560 --> 00:59:14.230
else's house?"When they walk in your

00:59:14.240 --> 00:59:16.310
home, what do you feel? Do demons push

00:59:16.320 --> 00:59:17.830
against you?

00:59:17.840 --> 00:59:23.190
Have you let critters in your house?

00:59:23.200 --> 00:59:26.030
What is so tangible in your home?

00:59:26.040 --> 00:59:28.350
I've been into some houses I can't

00:59:28.360 --> 00:59:30.390
wait to leave. I'm like, "I have got to

00:59:30.400 --> 00:59:32.510
get out of

00:59:32.510 --> 00:59:32.520
here."I've

00:59:32.520 --> 00:59:34.630
been into churches that I

00:59:34.630 --> 00:59:34.640
feel

00:59:34.640 --> 00:59:35.910
that.

00:59:35.920 --> 00:59:37.230
I said, "I got to get out of here right

00:59:37.240 --> 00:59:42.310
now."It

00:59:42.320 --> 00:59:45.510
pushes.

00:59:45.520 --> 00:59:46.670
But I'm trying to tell you, when you

00:59:46.680 --> 00:59:48.470
have him,

00:59:48.480 --> 00:59:50.430
there is a peace that passes all

00:59:50.440 --> 00:59:52.070
understanding

00:59:52.080 --> 00:59:53.750
and there's so much love and there's so

00:59:53.760 --> 00:59:55.110
much joy

00:59:55.120 --> 00:59:57.270
that will overflow your life, but you

00:59:57.280 --> 01:00:01.710
will be a carrier of it.

01:00:01.720 --> 01:00:02.990
You can feel presence. That's what I'm

01:00:03.000 --> 01:00:04.350
trying to tell you.

01:00:04.360 --> 01:00:06.950
Out of the overflow,

01:00:06.960 --> 01:00:08.510
that's why I try to be around certain

01:00:08.520 --> 01:00:10.830
people. I say, "My goodness, I feel his

01:00:10.840 --> 01:00:12.950
presence around you.

01:00:12.960 --> 01:00:15.750
I'll sow into

01:00:15.750 --> 01:00:15.760
it."I'm

01:00:15.760 --> 01:00:17.270
always curious about when somebody

01:00:17.280 --> 01:00:18.950
gives me money, especially when somebody

01:00:18.960 --> 01:00:20.430
wants to bless my family on this

01:00:20.440 --> 01:00:21.710
channel

01:00:21.720 --> 01:00:24.630
and I pray. I never ask for a dime.

01:00:24.640 --> 01:00:26.750
Never ask for a dime and never will.

01:00:26.760 --> 01:00:28.310
But there's people that feel led to give

01:00:28.320 --> 01:00:30.230
to us and say, "Hey, I feel led to help

01:00:30.240 --> 01:00:31.230
you."And

01:00:31.240 --> 01:00:32.710
I say,

01:00:32.710 --> 01:00:32.720
"Okay."But

01:00:32.720 --> 01:00:36.310
I always take and pray over their

01:00:36.320 --> 01:00:39.670
stuff. And I spend a lot of time

01:00:39.680 --> 01:00:41.190
and my wife will write them a

01:00:41.200 --> 01:00:42.630
letter or whatever,

01:00:42.640 --> 01:00:46.670
but I lay my hands on it and I

01:00:46.680 --> 01:00:49.590
intercede and I ask for God to multiply

01:00:49.600 --> 01:00:52.510
it because I look at it as special

01:00:52.520 --> 01:00:54.510
that somebody would work really hard to

01:00:54.520 --> 01:00:56.510
try to help me.

